casebody.data:
Lisa E. CARLOCK, Appellant,
v.
STATE of Missouri, Respondent. WD 81652 Missouri Court of Appeals, Western District. Order filed: May 28, 2019 Katharine P. Curry, for Appellant. Mary H. Moore, for Respondent. Before Division Three: Thomas H. Newton, Presiding Judge, Anthony Rex Gabbert, Judge and Edward R. Ardini, Jr., Judge

ORDER

PER CURIAM:

Lisa Carlock appeals the judgment of the Circuit Court of Pettis County denying her Rule 24.035 motion for post-conviction relief. Finding no error, we affirm. Because a published opinion would have no precedential value, we have instead provided a memorandum of law to the parties. Rule 84.16(b).
